title: Boeing Commercial delivers solid 2Q as demand remains strong | Manufacturers
text:
Boeing remains confident that it will not have to cut its 777 production rate as part of the transition to the 777X and maintains that overall demand for its commercial aircraft line continues to be rock-solid, dismissing unevenness that saw first-half orders lag behind ...
